24
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:21,900
and armchair speculation.

25
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:26,500
It might be plausible, he writes, that the BP oil spill caused this slowdown and that

26
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:33,180
