27
00:01:33,180 --> 00:01:35,300
What evidence is there for any of this?

28
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:36,300
None.

29
00:01:36,300 --> 00:01:38,220
It's just Zangari's ponderings.

30
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:43,260
